## Proposed Changes :   



**MultiHead Attention:**  




* **SelfAttention Layer**: Implement two parallel paths - one using traditional Conv operation (`PW`) & BatchNorm + SiLu activation, another employing Multi Head Self Attentions (“MHSA”) over feature maps generated via previous “Dw” Convolutional Operation.** Connect both outputs at ResADD stage before moving further into subsequent Layers.<br> <p/>





 * Add an additional parameter named "mhsa" during module initialization which dictates whether MHSA will utilize features extracted solely form 'Pw’ output OR combine them wtih those derived directly From ‘Lw’.<P />







### Implementation Details:<BR><Br>- Replace ``padding`` calculations utilizing fixed padding formula provided previously ('PadNumX') With dynamic paddings computed dynamically according To head number (‘Heads’) leveraging TFPad functionality.(This ensures consistent behavior across various numbers Of Heads)<a href="transformer/">Transformer Padding Techniques </ref>.






